Products.FullDescription: Continental Pasta & Sauce Creamy Bacon Carbonara
Products.RichDescription:
CONTINENTAL PASTA & SAUCE CREAMY BACON CARBONARA 85 GR

Create the taste of Italy in your very kitchen with this Creamy Bacon Carbonara Pasta & Sauce, it’s sure to become a classic in your weekly repertoire. Pasta & Sauces are available in a standard size or a value pack. How to Prepare: Cooking time: 10 minutes Stove top - for best results 1) Bring ¾ cup (190mL) Lite milk, 1 cup (250mL) hot water, 1 teaspoon Flora Salt Reduced spread and Pasta & Sauce pack contents to the boil, stirring 2) Simmer, uncovered for 10 minutes, stirring regularly until sauce thickens and pasta is cooked Microwave (900W) – cooking times may vary 1) Combine ¾ cup (190mL) Lite milk, 1 cup (250mL) hot water, 1 teaspoon Flora Salt Reduced spread and Pasta & Sauce pack contents in a microwave safe bowl 2) Cook uncovered on HIGH for 10-12 minutes, stirring 2-3 times. Stand 2 minutes before serving. Cook a complete meal in 15 minutes. Go to our website for delicious one pan meal ideas. At Continental, we love food the way you do. We know how much you value good, nutritious, flavourful food, as well as authentic home cooking. It feels good to cook, and even better to bring pleasure to the ones you love, through the food you put on the table. For over 50 years now, our chefs at Continental have combined their expertise, love of flavour, and only the finest ingredients to help you create great tasting meals every day.

No artificial colours

No artificial flavours

No added MSG

Packed with flavour

Serves 3

Products.RichDescription:
CONTINENTAL RICE CHEESY 125 GR 
 Continental Classic Cheesy Rice dish takes no time at all to cook. Serve this Cheesy Rice dish as a side dish or create a tasty dinner meal with one of our simple recipe bases. How to Prepare this Continental Cheesy Rice meal: Cooking time: 10 minutes. Stove top - for best results 1) Bring 1¼ cups (310mL) hot water, 1 teaspoon Flora Salt Reduced spread and Seasoned Rice pack contents to the boil, stirring 2) Cover and simmer for 10 minutes. Remove from heat. Stir, replace lid and stand for 2 minutes. For Microwave (900W) – cooking times may vary 1) Combine 1½ cups (375mL) hot water, 1 teaspoon Flora Salt Reduced spread and Seasoned Rice pack contents in a microwave safe bowl 2) Cover and cook on HIGH for 8-10 minutes. Stir, replace cover and stand for 2 minutes before serving. Cook a complete side dish or dinner meal in 15 minutes. At Continental, we love food the way you do. We know how much you value good, nutritious, flavourful food, as well as authentic home cooking. It feels good to cook, and even better to bring pleasure to the ones you love, through the food you put on the table. For over 50 years now, our chefs at Continental have combined their expertise, love of flavour, and only the finest ingredients to help you create great tasting meals every day.
 Continental Classic Cheesy Rice is made with 100% sustainably grown Australian rice. 
 Continental Classic Cheesy Rice has no artificial flavours. 
 Continental Classic Cheesy Rice has no added MSG. 
 Continental Classic Cheesy Rice is packed with flavour. 
 Continental Classic Cheesy Rice has no artificial colours.

Products.RichDescription:
CONTINENTAL PASTA & SAUCE ALFREDO GARLIC HERB 85 GR

In just a few easy steps, create a delicious mid-week meal the whole family will enjoy, with the help of Continental. This delicious Alfredo with Garlic & Herbs Pasta & Sauce combines creamy tasty cheese, garlic, parsley and oregano. To this we add our pasta, made from responsibly Australian grown wheat using the traditional Italian recipe. It’s freshly made and then dried for 4 hours so it maintains its firmness for the perfect al dente pasta. Cooking our Pasta Alfredo with fresh milk gives you the classic creamy taste but with a signature light consistency. All our Continental pasta and sauces contain no artificial colours, flavours or added MSG. How to Prepare: Cooking time: 10 minutes Stove top - for best results 1) Bring 1 cup (250mL) Lite milk, ¾ cup (190mL) hot water, 1 teaspoon Flora Salt Reduced spread and Pasta & Sauce pack contents to the boil, stirring 2) Simmer, uncovered for 10 minutes, stirring regularly until sauce thickens and pasta is cooked Microwave (900W) – cooking times may vary 1) Combine 1 cup (250mL) Lite milk, ¾ cup (190mL) hot water, 1 teaspoon Flora Salt Reduced spread and Pasta & Sauce pack contents in a microwave safe bowl 2) Cook uncovered on HIGH for 10-12 minutes, stirring 2-3 times. Stand 2 minutes before serving. Cook a complete meal in 15 minutes.

No artificial colours

No artificial flavours

No added MSG

Packed with flavour

Serves 3
